org.glassfish.api.admingui

Interface ConsoleProvider

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CDIEventBusNotifierPlugin, ClusterConsolePlugin, CommonUtilPlugin, ConcurrentConsolePlugin, CorbaConsolePlugin, DatadogNotifierPlugin, EjbConsolePlugin, EjbLiteConsolePlugin, EmailNotifierPlugin, EventBusNotifierPlugin, HealthcheckServicePlugin, HipChatNotifierPlugin, JcaConsolePlugin, JdbcConsolePlugin, JMailConsolePlugin, JmsNotifierPlugin, JmxMonitoringPlugin, JtsConsolePlugin, NewRelicNotifierPlugin, OSGIConsoleProvider, PayaraConsolePlugin, PluginConsoleProvider, SlackNotifierPlugin, SNMPNotifierPlugin, SupportPlugin, ThemePlugin, WebConsolePlugin, XmppNotifierPlugin

    @Contract
public interface ConsoleProvider

    This interface exists to provide a marker for locating modules which provide GUI features to be displayed in the GlassFish admin console. The getConfiguration() method should either return (null), or a URL to the console-config.xml file.

    Author:
    Ken Paulsen (ken.paulsen@sun.com)

    • Method Detail

      • getConfiguration

        URL getConfiguration()

        Returns a URL to the console-config.xml file, or null. If null is returned, the default (DEFAULT_CONFIG_FILENAME) will be used.
